@startuml
title UML state machine diagram

state "Choose/Enter Withdrawal Amount" as ChooseAmount
ChooseAmount : entry/User selects or inputs amount
ChooseAmount : do/Shows predefined amounts for selection
ChooseAmount : do/Allows user to input custom amount
ChooseAmount : exit/Proceed with transaction

state "Cancel Transaction" as CancelTransaction
CancelTransaction : entry/User wants to cancel
CancelTransaction : do/Stops the transaction
CancelTransaction : exit/Returns card and ends session

state "Withdrawal" as Withdrawal
Withdrawal : entry/Proceeds with transaction
Withdrawal : do/Processes withdrawal amount
Withdrawal : exit/Dispenses cash and updates balance

state J1 <<choice>>

[*] --> J1

J1 --> ChooseAmount

ChooseAmount --> Withdrawal
ChooseAmount --> CancelTransaction

@enduml
